          <li><strong>Industry</strong>: segment accounts by business type for targeted pipeline management</li>
          <li><strong>Account Tier</strong>: classify VIP and high-value customers for prioritised service</li>
          <li><strong>Customer Since</strong>: track relationship longevity to support renewal and upsell workflows</li>
          <li><strong>Billing and Shipping Addresses</strong>: separate address fields for order fulfilment accuracy</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="overflow-hidden">
          <img src="/assets/account-fields.jpg" alt="Salesforce Account custom fields configuration" class="w-full h-auto" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-10">
        <h4 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3" style="color: var(--blue);">Opportunity Object</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-1.5 text-sm mb-6 list-none" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">
