          <li><strong>Lead Source</strong>: track deal origin for marketing attribution and ROI reporting</li>
          <li><strong>Discount Percentage</strong>: enable customer-specific pricing within Salesforce CPQ workflows</li>
          <li><strong>Payment Terms</strong>: capture Net 30, Net 60, and other terms for finance and fulfilment</li>
